************ShortCutKey***********
ctrl+shift+/ for comment in one line
and ctrl+shift+C remove comment  



*********
command to delete files from root
root@ginger-Vostro-3668:/usr/share# rm -r -f tomcat

**********
command to go to root from user
sudo -i
and from root to user
exit

**************
command to change permission from root
 home/ginger/tomcat# chmod -R 777 /home/ginger/tomcat
**************
command to extract a file

suppose file is in opt folder
/opt# tar xvzf a.tar.gz

**************
command to know ports used by different tcp and ip

top

**************
command to kill that service at specific port
  sudo kill 4198

